learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-10T18:58:21.251Z",context-specialist,"Upstream pm CLI UX bug: repeated --section/--id flags do not accumulate into arrays; only the last value is kept. Workaround: use comma-separated values (--section focus,blockers). Affects all pm extensions with repeatable string flags."
